  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>GameInfo</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In a post-apocalyptic world following a virus outbreak, human civilization has collapsed. You will play as a lone survivor, struggling to stay alive in a small village surrounded by zombies. The village’s resources are nearly exhausted, with most of the remaining supplies either spoiled or contaminated by zombies. Your mission is to survive under extreme conditions, not only by scavenging for supplies but also by avoiding infection and finding hope for escape amid the relentless threat of incoming zombies.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This is a two-player cooperative survival game where you and your partner must rely on mutual trust and flawless teamwork to overcome hordes of zombies and find the only way out. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >It’s not just a survival game; it’s also a dual test of coordination and intelligence. Together, you’ll face unexpected challenges and devise the best strategies to turn danger into opportunity.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Guide</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3349930/extras/bbee6052f1cf4013a7afd77756d1af5d.avif?t=1746014298\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3349930/extras_big/bbee6052f1cf4013a7afd77756d1af5d.avif?t=1746014298 width=800 height=372 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3349930/extras/1a4c841fefb94e6106f31a95a986e897.avif?t=1746014298\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3349930/extras_big/1a4c841fefb94e6106f31a95a986e897.avif?t=1746014298 width=800 height=350 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3349930/extras/43557faf663719eeb624f9f0952e090c.avif?t=1746014298\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3349930/extras_big/43557faf663719eeb624f9f0952e090c.avif?t=1746014298 width=800 height=340 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3349930/extras/df37abd4ef0c333474114d9b892c287a.avif?t=1746014298\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3349930/extras_big/df37abd4ef0c333474114d9b892c287a.avif?t=1746014298 width=800 height=336 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3349930/extras/f9bdcf7cdbe42349061fb94a7570c21f.avif?t=1746014298\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3349930/extras_big/f9bdcf7cdbe42349061fb94a7570c21f.avif?t=1746014298 width=800 height=346 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Control</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3349930/extras/f45d0430249e190fb5737fd68e5b1737.avif?t=1746014298\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3349930/extras_big/f45d0430249e190fb5737fd68e5b1737.avif?t=1746014298 width=800 height=424 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3349930/extras/9aa1fd55ee6a0a300d41361b4c5245a2.avif?t=1746014298\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3349930/extras_big/9aa1fd55ee6a0a300d41361b4c5245a2.avif?t=1746014298 width=800 height=418 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Cross-Platform Support</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Windows</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Full support for keyboard and game controllers</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >macOS</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Full support for keyboard and game controllers</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>GameInfo</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In a post-apocalyptic world following a virus outbreak, human civilization has collapsed. You will play as a lone survivor, struggling to stay alive in a small village surrounded by zombies. The village’s resources are nearly exhausted, with most of the remaining supplies either spoiled or contaminated by zombies. Your mission is to survive under extreme conditions, not only by scavenging for supplies but also by avoiding infection and finding hope for escape amid the relentless threat of incoming zombies.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This is a two-player cooperative survival game where you and your partner must rely on mutual trust and flawless teamwork to overcome hordes of zombies and find the only way out. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >It’s not just a survival game; it’s also a dual test of coordination and intelligence. Together, you’ll face unexpected challenges and devise the best strategies to turn danger into opportunity.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Guide</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3349930/extras/bbee6052f1cf4013a7afd77756d1af5d.avif?t=1746014298\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3349930/extras_big/bbee6052f1cf4013a7afd77756d1af5d.avif?t=1746014298 width=800 height=372 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3349930/extras/1a4c841fefb94e6106f31a95a986e897.avif?t=1746014298\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3349930/extras_big/1a4c841fefb94e6106f31a95a986e897.avif?t=1746014298 width=800 height=350 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.ak